prompt: My father passed away quite recently, and a week or so after he was gone I wanted to make a video of him, as a way of saying goodbye. I didn't know what song to choose, I could've picked a song that he liked, but Seasons just came to my mind, so I used this music for the video. I know the meaning of the lyrics are more on the romantic side, but I don't know, something about it just reminds me of my dad. Now, when I'm randomly listening to my playlist, and this music starts to play, I feel hugged by my dad, and always have to hold in the tears. Thank you so much for this song, Wave to Earth ❤
